36:54.000 --> 36:56.000
What is the meaning of it?

36:56.000 --> 36:58.000
It is a return on investment

36:58.000 --> 37:00.000
for buying a product.

37:00.000 --> 37:02.000
A rebate program is a return

37:02.000 --> 37:04.000
on investment

37:04.000 --> 37:06.000
for a certain amount of money.

37:06.000 --> 37:08.000
For example, you say that your product costs

37:08.000 --> 37:10.000
1,000 rubles, but if you buy

37:10.000 --> 37:12.000
a batch of 1,000 pieces,

37:12.000 --> 37:14.000
we will give you a 15% discount.

37:14.000 --> 37:16.000
That is, we will return 150 rubles

37:16.000 --> 37:18.000
from each product.

37:18.000 --> 37:20.000
But this will only happen if you buy

37:20.000 --> 37:22.000
a certain amount.

37:22.000 --> 37:24.000
The client says, yes, I will buy it,

37:24.000 --> 37:26.000
but I am not ready to do it right away

37:26.000 --> 37:28.000
because it is immediate investment.

37:28.000 --> 37:30.000
He says, I will do it

37:30.000 --> 37:32.000
within three months or a year.

37:32.000 --> 37:34.000
But if you give him a discount in advance,

37:34.000 --> 37:36.000
where is the guarantee

37:36.000 --> 37:38.000
that he will buy it from you?

37:38.000 --> 37:40.000
Yes, he signed the contract,

37:40.000 --> 37:42.000
yes, he promised you,

37:42.000 --> 37:44.000
he will definitely do it.

37:44.000 --> 37:46.000
In the end, he will tell you, well, he could not.

37:46.000 --> 37:48.000
What will you do with it?

37:48.000 --> 37:50.000
Such a rebate discount or retro bonus

37:50.000 --> 37:52.000
is a guarantee that

37:52.000 --> 37:54.000
he will either buy

37:54.000 --> 37:56.000
this turnover

37:56.000 --> 37:58.000
or you will not pay him

37:58.000 --> 38:00.000
extra money.

38:00.000 --> 38:02.000
And this discount that you will have to pay him

38:02.000 --> 38:04.000
will work for you for a whole year.

38:04.000 --> 38:06.000
That is, it will be money in the turnover of your company.

38:06.000 --> 38:08.000
This is also a plus.

38:08.000 --> 38:10.000
And, in fact, at the end of the period

38:10.000 --> 38:12.000
when the client buys the entire batch

38:12.000 --> 38:14.000
that he promised,

38:14.000 --> 38:16.000
you return this amount to him

38:16.000 --> 38:18.000
without cash,

38:18.000 --> 38:20.000
which you promised,

38:20.000 --> 38:22.000
150 rubles from each product.

38:22.000 --> 38:24.000
And this is either a retro bonus or a rebate program,

38:24.000 --> 38:26.000
whatever you call it.

38:26.000 --> 38:28.000
What is interesting,

38:28.000 --> 38:30.000
in Russia this is mainly used on the trade channel,

38:30.000 --> 38:32.000
and in the West,

38:32.000 --> 38:34.000
such a system is very actively used

38:34.000 --> 38:36.000
by retail stores, retail networks.

38:36.000 --> 38:38.000
For example,

38:38.000 --> 38:40.000
