38:48.000 --> 38:50.000
in the same store,

38:50.000 --> 38:52.000
but you cannot take it with money.

38:52.000 --> 38:54.000
Thus, you are forced to return to this store

38:54.000 --> 38:56.000
one way or another,

38:56.000 --> 38:58.000
become a more loyal,

38:58.000 --> 39:00.000
constant client to it.

39:00.000 --> 39:02.000
The next point I would like to talk about

39:02.000 --> 39:04.000
is the so-called MDF funds.

39:04.000 --> 39:06.000
Market Development Fund.

39:06.000 --> 39:08.000
What are these funds?

39:08.000 --> 39:10.000
You agree with your intermediaries

39:10.000 --> 39:12.000
literally on the following.

39:12.000 --> 39:14.000
If they buy a certain product

39:14.000 --> 39:16.000
in a certain amount,

39:16.000 --> 39:18.000
you give them an additional discount.

39:18.000 --> 39:20.000
But you do not give them a discount with money.

39:20.000 --> 39:22.000
You accumulate this discount

39:22.000 --> 39:24.000
on your account.

39:24.000 --> 39:26.000
A virtual account is created

39:26.000 --> 39:28.000
at the client and accumulated.

39:28.000 --> 39:30.000
The sales manager must follow this account.

39:30.000 --> 39:32.000
Why?

39:32.000 --> 39:34.000
Because the sales manager

39:34.000 --> 39:36.000
must follow the sales manager.

39:36.000 --> 39:38.000
What will this money be used for?

39:38.000 --> 39:40.000
To promote the product

39:40.000 --> 39:42.000
on the client's territory.

39:42.000 --> 39:44.000
What usually happens?

39:44.000 --> 39:46.000
Our intermediaries do not have money

39:46.000 --> 39:48.000
to promote our product.

39:48.000 --> 39:50.000
They are not very interested in this.

39:50.000 --> 39:52.000
They say, promote yourself if you need to.

39:52.000 --> 39:54.000
And we are interested in promoting the product.

39:54.000 --> 39:56.000
So, we offer an additional discount,

39:56.000 --> 39:58.000
accumulate the amount.

39:58.000 --> 40:00.000
If this amount is accumulated,

40:00.000 --> 40:02.000
then the intermediary can use it

40:02.000 --> 40:04.000
as a marketing budget

40:04.000 --> 40:06.000
to promote our product

40:06.000 --> 40:08.000
on their market.

40:08.000 --> 40:10.000
He promotes not only our product,

40:10.000 --> 40:12.000
but also his company.

40:12.000 --> 40:14.000
Therefore, in any case,

40:14.000 --> 40:16.000
he should be interested.

40:16.000 --> 40:18.000
According to the rules,

40:18.000 --> 40:20.000
you should say that you do not pay for this with money.

