40:54.000 --> 40:56.000
There was a very interesting example.

40:56.000 --> 40:58.000
A company for the production of office chairs.

40:58.000 --> 41:00.000
It has distributors.

41:00.000 --> 41:02.000
One of the distributors

41:02.000 --> 41:04.000
