41:20.000 --> 41:22.000
Can you imagine?

41:22.000 --> 41:24.000
There was a screen on the Internet

41:24.000 --> 41:26.000
on Yandex

41:26.000 --> 41:28.000
when a young person

41:28.000 --> 41:30.000
sits in a chair

41:30.000 --> 41:32.000
