01:47:44.000 --> 01:47:46.000
the effectiveness of the share.

01:47:46.000 --> 01:47:48.000
It is the definition of the share loss

01:47:48.000 --> 01:47:50.000
in the additional product turnover.

01:47:50.000 --> 01:47:52.000
What is the point of this calculation?

01:47:52.000 --> 01:47:54.000
For example, you sold the product

01:47:54.000 --> 01:47:56.000
